{{Quote|Apsolon used to have a totalitarian government ruling over a civilization split between a prosperous minority called the Civilized and a majority called the Workers.|[[Tahl]]|<ref name="Jedi Apprentice: The Ties That Bind">''[[Jedi Apprentice: The Ties That Bind]]''</ref>}}
The '''Civilized''' was the collective name of a group representing members of specific political, economical, and social classes that lived on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[New Apsolon/Legends|New Apsolon]]. In contrast with the [[Workers]], who were a group representing the poorer inhabitants of the planet, the Civilized were the highest and wealthiest caste, living in houses constructed of stone [[Mining/Legends|mined]] from the outskirts of the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]]. The Civilized were staunch political opponents of the Workers.

